Wild at Heart Season 4 Episode 9
--------------------------------
- Synopsis: In the aftermath of the storm, Rowan takes charge of the situation as 
            the residents try to free Charlotte from beneath the rubble and rescue 
            Danny, who has been left behind by Alice in her desperate search for 
            help. Vanessa and Rowan use a helicopter to eventually spot him lying 
            unconscious in the Bush and take him home. The next morning, Alice 
            decides to pack her bags and leave, but a kiss from Danny might prompt 
            a change of heart.
